{"sn56.20:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 56.20 ","sn56.20:0.2":"2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga ","sn56.20:0.3":"Tathasutta ","sn56.20:1.1":"“Cattarimani, bhikkhave, tathani avitathani anannathani. ","sn56.20:1.2":"Katamani cattari? ","sn56.20:1.3":"‘Idam dukkhan’ti, bhikkhave, tathametam avitathametam anannathametam; ","sn56.20:1.4":"‘ayam dukkhasamudayo’ti tathametam avitathametam anannathametam; ","sn56.20:1.5":"‘ayam dukkhanirodho’ti tathametam avitathametam anannathametam; ","sn56.20:1.6":"‘ayam dukkhanirodhagamini patipada’ti tathametam avitathametam anannathametam—","sn56.20:1.7":"imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari tathani avitathani anannathani. ","sn56.20:2.1":"Tasmatiha, bhikkhave, ‘idam dukkhan’ti yogo karaniyo …pe… ‘ayam dukkhanirodhagamini patipada’ti yogo karaniyo”ti. ","sn56.20:2.2":"Dasamam. ","sn56.20:2.3":"Dhammacakkappavattanavaggo dutiyo. ","sn56.20:3.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn56.20:3.1":"Dhammacakkam tathagatam, ","sn56.20:3.2":"khandha ayatanena ca; ","sn56.20:3.3":"Dharana ca dve avijja, ","sn56.20:3.4":"vijja sankasana tathati. "}